Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又投身政變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍人的楷模如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米盧諾夫大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次戰斗 如果我遇到不測
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.15,0:22:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我不知道該如何面對封閉了心靈的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還有什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫莉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米盧諾夫大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.15,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道升降機倒塌之後4個月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂世之中人們只能任由飄零麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 交錯的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰火之中 誰人之吶喊
